description: Wine 9.3 has landed as another early development release of the Windows compatibility layer on the road to Wine 10 next year. Here's the highlights of what's changed.
title: Wine 9.3 out now with Internet Proxy support improvements, New HID pointer device driver

description: Valve announced that Proton 9.0 is now available for testing, with lots of game compatibility improvements for Steam Deck and Desktop Linux thanks to it now being based on the recent Wine 9.0 release.
title: Proton 9.0 now in Beta with improved game compatibility for Steam Deck / Linux
